dc_title_s: EMS Response Districts Jackson County, WI 2020
dc_description_s: This data layer represents Emergency Medical Service (EMS) response districts in Jackson County, Wisconsin in 2020. [This digital geospatial dataset is a current representation of all Ambulance Service Zones in Jackson County, Wisconsin, with attributes standardized in accordance to the NENA Standard for NG9-1-1 GIS Data Model (NENA-STA-006.1-2018). Responding Ambulance Services include Black River Ambulance Services, Gold Cross Ambulance Services, Tomah Area Ambulance Services, and Gunderson Tri-State Ambulance Services.]
